{"tid":1496311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「香港咁少人做會計？」823呀！12:30 準時入數啦","createTime":"2019-08-22T12:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T06:15:52.000Z","uid":288571,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c17a1981b532080d2f998b1bf54775f1c29c9f29","tid":1496311,"uid":288571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:52:28.000Z","msg":"首先我係P牌，求大家幫推，麻煩貼多d文宣圖！感謝巴絲們<br />\n<br />\n（轉分享）<br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》的爭議持續，並引發多次的警民衝突。政府作為爭議的始作俑者，未有採取積極措施平息紛爭，修補市民與政府之間的關係，表現令人失望。<br />\n<br />\n會計師作為香港社會的一員，有責任站出來，以專業人士的身份要求政府正視社會的訴求，解決現時的紛爭。我們現發起8月23日的會計界遊行，要求政府接受民間提出的五大訴求：1. 完全撤回修訂《逃犯條例》的法案、2. 撤回612集會的暴動定性、3. 停止追究反送中示威者、4. 成立獨立委員會，徹查警察處理示威活動及元朗暴力事件的手法、5. 全面落實雙真普選。<br />\n<br />\n8月23日會計界遊行<br />\n時間：12:30集合<br />\n遊行路線：中環遮打花園至金鐘政府總部<br />\n註：是次遊行已獲警方發出不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kennethleung.legco/photos/a.380611092004190/2366093530122593?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkennethleung.legco%2Fphotos%2Fa.380611092004190%2F2366093530122593%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=33794084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kennethleung.legco/photos/a.380611092004190/2366093530122593?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"1b00a5f5be35ee8f8b833d09122780c3292f8f42","tid":1496311,"uid":288571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:53:10.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"1f58ddc5be2292488579576ca16aa3ef8cb14a84","tid":1496311,"uid":288571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"自推9"},{"pid":"ae2d203ea7bd913f9f1808ac3f96201efcb80856","tid":1496311,"uid":288571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:58:47.000Z","msg":"自推8"},{"pid":"6298682f6c0561eda017af1bf64816b99b609f7e","tid":1496311,"uid":296112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:00:38.000Z","msg":"推！ 聽日見<img src=\"/as